<title>NETHERLANDS: VAN MELLE FIRST-HALF NET RISES.</title>
<headline>VAN MELLE FIRST-HALF NET RISES.</headline>
<dateline>BREDA, Netherlands 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30,</p>
<p>1996 (in millions of guilders unless otherwise stated)</p>
<p>    Net per shr (guilders)	     2.82 vs   2.63</p>
<p>    Net profit			    24.1  vs  22.3</p>
<p>    Turnover			     403    vs 361</p>
<p>    Operating profit		    32    vs  34</p>
<p>NOTE - Sweets maker Van Melle NV said in March it expected</p>
<p>1996 profits at a &quot;healthy level&quot; but gave no further forecast</p>
<p>    Interest gain			  3.3  vs   1.4 charge</p>
<p>    Tax				     10.3  vs   9.5</p>
<p>    Minorities charge		    0.6  vs   same</p>
<p>-- Amsterdam newsroom +31 20 504 5000, Fax +31 20 504 5040</p>
